  "detailed_description": "Create your character and start matching via the phone app. Buy new clothes, cars, houses to impress people. Set up a meeting with the person you match with the right dialogues. Earn money by working various jobs. Eat at the restaurant or have a drink at the bar. Try to establish the right dialogues according to the personality of the person in front of you. If you're in a low mood, you might consider going to a club.<br><br>A simulation game with a happy ending in bed.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Earn money and feel better by buying new vehicles.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709080/extras/8fb29b98a63c4acb76ab4c6a406cfcc8.poster.avif?t=1751967327\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709080/extras/8fb29b98a63c4acb76ab4c6a406cfcc8.webm?t=1751967327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709080/extras/8fb29b98a63c4acb76ab4c6a406cfcc8.mp4?t=1751967327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You're gonna want to go here.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709080/extras/b69af6443431fd0960f322f9e413eda7.poster.avif?t=1751967327\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709080/extras/b69af6443431fd0960f322f9e413eda7.webm?t=1751967327\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709080/extras/b69af6443431fd0960f322f9e413eda7.mp4?t=1751967327\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Are you unhappy with yourself? No problem, you can create your dream self here.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_c